No. 09-1187. Deanna McBrearty, et al., Petitioners v. The Vanguard Group, Inc., et al. 560 U.S. 979, 130 S. Ct. 3411,

177 L. Ed. 2d 349,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 4743. June 14, 2010.
